OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start with sunny spells
OL,6,Ffor many, before increasing cloud
OL,7,Fbrings a slight chance of showers,
OL,8,Fmainly over higher ground. Any showers
OL,9,Fwill be lighter and more isolated than
OL,10,Fon previous days, with winds
OL,11,Fcontinuing to ease.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny remaining showers will
OL,14,Ffade away, leaving a largely dry
OL,15,Fevening with light winds. Cloud will
OL,16,Fincrease from the west later, bringing
OL,17,Fa few outbreaks of rain before dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
