OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FMostly cloudy and rather
OL,6,Fgrey, with outbreaks of rain slowly
OL,7,Fmoving north-eastwards through the
OL,8,Fday. Some brighter intervals may
OL,9,Fdevelop later in the evening. Winds
OL,10,Fremaining light.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,13,Fcloudy and breezy on Sunday, some rain
OL,14,Fover hills. Band of rain moving east
OL,15,Fon Monday. Cooler and windy on
OL,16,FTuesday, with sunny spells and
OL,17,Fshowers, occasionally heavy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
